features: 【600W Powerful Motor & 18000Pa Suction】INSE corded vacuum cleaner is equipped with a 600W strong motor, can generate up to 18000Pa powerful suction, is perfect for hardwood floors, marble floors, tile, low pile carpet and can easily pick up all kinds of particles like dust, pet hair, pet litter, cereal, etc.

【6-in-1 Multifunction with Versatile Tools】The stick vacuum cleaner is easy to assemble and it has 3 different attachment heads - main floor brush & crevice tool & 2-in-1 brush, which can have 6 versatile combinations. When converted from a stick vacuum cleaner to a handheld vacuum cleaner, it performs decently on corners, stairs, shelves, and even on your car.

【High-Efficient Filtration with Extra Filter】The vacuum cleaner filters and captures up to 99.99% of microparticles and expels cleaner air, providing a clean and healthy home for your family. An extra filter is provided as a backup, regularly cleaning or replacing the filter can maintain the powerful suction. (Please make sure to use the vacuum cleaner with the filter.)

【Adjustable Rod and Long Power Cord】This vacuum allows 23ft of long-distance cleaning, no need to worry about running out of power. The lightweight vacuum cleaner tube can be adjusted from 19 to 31 inches, suitable for all family members. One click can start the vacuum, and one simple press can empty the 1L dust cup. The filter is washable and reusable, please leave it dry before refitting.

【Tangle Free Design and Accessories Hook】The main floor brush reduces the tangled issue of hair with no beater roller design. The vacuum cleaner corded comes with a tiny storage hook that can be attached to the tube to store accessories, very space-saving and convenient.
【Worry-free Warranty】Each INSE vacuum cleaner is well-made and we back it with a 12-month warranty and professional customer support, please buy with confidence.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 100% what I was looking for
reviews.reviewText: So I drive an 18-wheeler and any trucker will tell you that it is hard to keep your floor clean. I've tried a bunch of different battery powered, or portable, vacuums and they all stink. I do have an APU (onboard diesel generator) so I have access to outlet power. I wanted something super small that I could keep in one of the small drawers but had enough power to actually pick stuff off my floor. This does just that. It is super cheaply made, if I used it for more than 5 minutes a day I'm sure it wouldn't last very long, but for the price I paid I would 100% buy it again. This does a great job of picking up all the little rocks you get from going through gravel shippers and has enough suction to pull all of the dirt out of the little nooks and crannies.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 26, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Should’ve known better
reviews.reviewText: I was hesitant to purchase this item not because of the low price but for the simple fact that they would show the entire vacuum. The biggest disappointment is that there is no roller on this unit.Now I understand that some people don’t want the roller but I do. My entire house is hardwood floors but I have found that the rollers made for smooth floors does a lot better than those without.Though this vacuum did everything it said, the suction wasn’t as powerful as one would need. The bottom design didn’t allow for complete pickup and you have to go over more than once to pick up everything. The motor got hot enough to burn you andthough the the swivel is good on the head, it will not allow you to lay the vacuum flat to get under low furniture as the lower you go the vacuum begins to lift off the floor.It’s an ok vacuum for basic pickup but anything further that will have you looking elsewhere.Here’s the kicker. You won’t see this on Amazon or their selling page but I received this email from them after my purchase even before I received the product. Catch what it says…Many thanks for your purchase! Hope our vacuum cleaner can be your effective assistant for cleaning.*NOTE: Due to powerful suction and high power, it might be easy to fit tightly with high-pile carpet, so it is not suitable for use on thick carpets, perfect for hard floors.Here are other 3 notes about using a corded vacuum cleaner:1. Please clean the brush, filter, and dust box regularly to keep the maximum suction, and please don't forget to put the inlet filter pad back after fully air drying.2. It's common that the temperature of the motor part is higher than in other parts during use. Please don't worry, INSE I5 has a high-power motor to provide decent suction, and it features over-heating protection for safe use.3. If vacuum loses sution or shuts off suddenly. Please clean the filters and the blockage in time, wait for a few minutes to let the motor cool down, and it can start again.
